These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
Nationality: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
City: nizza, new-york, hannover, rome
1. City:rome is not to the right of City:nizza##8
2. City:rome is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1
3. Nationality:chinese is on the left or right of Nationality:german##3
4. Nationality:mexican is somewhere to the right of City:new-york##5
5. Nationality:mexican is not to the left of City:rome##8
6. City:hannover is somewhere to the left of Nationality:chinese##5
7. Nationality:chinese is somewhere between Nationality:brazilian and City:new-york##7
8. Nationality:chinese and City:rome have the same parity positions##9
9. Nationality:german and City:nizza have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | hannover   | rome     | new-york | nizza  |

