.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
Game: chess, canasta, bridge, whist
Hobby: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. Hobby:dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:traveling and Game:canasta have the same parity positions##9
3. Hobby:drawing is not to the right of Hobby:sudoku##8
4. Hobby:dancing is not to the right of Game:whist##8
5. Hobby:dancing is somewhere to the left of Game:chess##5
6. Game:chess is somewhere to the right of Hobby:drawing##5
7. Game:canasta is somewhere to the right of Game:chess##5
8. Game:whist is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | whist     | bridge    | chess | canasta    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

