.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, dancing, drawing
Music-Genre: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. Music-Genre:hip-hop == Hobby:magic-tricks##1
2. Music-Genre:indie is on the right of Music-Genre:reggae##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is somewhere to the left of Hobby:magic-tricks##5
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left or right of Hobby:dancing##3
5. Music-Genre:indie is on the left of Hobby:gardening##1
6. Hobby:drawing and Music-Genre:trance have the same parity positions##9
7. Hobby:dancing is on the left or right of Hobby:gardening##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | drawing | dancing | gardening  | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

