.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
House: ranch-style, cottage, modern, farmhouse
Pet: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. House:modern != Pet:hedgehog##6
2. Pet:cat and House:ranch-style have different parity positions##9
3. Pet:dog and House:cottage have different parity positions##9
4. Pet:dog is somewhere to the left of House:modern##5
5. Pet:cat is on the left of House:farmhouse##1
6. House:cottage != Pet:dog##6
7. House:farmhouse is somewhere to the left of House:cottage##5
8. Pet:cat is on the right of House:ranch-style##1
9. Pet:pony != House:farmhouse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | ranch-style | modern | farmhouse  | cottage |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

