 4. Food:radish is in an odd position##4
 5. Food:nectarine != Beverage:cola##6
 6. Beverage:water is not to the right of Beverage:coffee##8
 7. Beverage:water and Food:radish have the same parity positions##9
 8. Beverage:cola is not to the right of Beverage:juice##8
 9. Beverage:water == Food:radish##1
10. Beverage:cola and Food:radish have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | pepper | corn | radish | nectarine |

 